# caian 04/11/2015

Language Definition

Reserved Words:

    prog    program definition to this language

    begin   begin bracket
    end     end bracket

    fix     constant declaration

    ary     array declaration

    :       definition

Variables Types:
    Usage
        <type>:x
        <type>:y=<value>
    
    int     integer
    dob     double
    bl      boolean
    str     string

Loops:
    Usage
        while(<expression>)
        begin
        end

    while   while loop

Conditional:
    Usage
        if(<expression>)
        begin
        end

    if      conditional

R/W:
    Usage
        str:f=read(<file_name>)
        write(<file_name>,f)

    read    read file
    write   write file

Algebric:
    +       sum
    -       less
    *       multiply
    /       division
    =       equal

Logical:
    >       greater
    !=      diffrent
    not     not
    and     and
    or      or
